    "title": " 关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体开店管理规则》公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1321438418332127232",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展，针对《</span><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=915118822988582912\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"color: #1400ff;\"><u>京东开放平台个人/个体开店管理规则</u></span></span></a></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">》</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行调整<span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年12月25日- 2025年12月31日，规则预计于2026年1月1日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">核心调整点：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">调整展示位置，删除附表1中，\"0元试运营阶段\"一列，在正文第十三条（一）中，以附表形式展示支持0元试运营的所有类目。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">修订后内容如下：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">第十三条 保证金缴纳</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">（一）&ldquo;0元&rdquo;试运营</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">针对新入驻的个人/个体店铺商家，部分类目支持&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营，即入驻不缴纳保证金，待进入正式运营阶段后再缴纳保证金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #c55a11;\">参与&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营的类目可详见：0元试运营类目明细。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #c55a11;\">注：具体明细以最终公示为准。</span></p>",
